    nursingActions: ["Perform comprehensive cranial nerve assessment", "Assess extraocular movements (6 cardinal positions of gaze)", "Monitor for signs of peritonsillar abscess (trismus, uvular deviation)", "Assess vestibular function (nystagmus, vertigo)", "Monitor post-tonsillectomy for bleeding (frequent swallowing)", "Evaluate swallowing function before oral intake", "Report sudden vision changes immediately"],
